OL,3,CGuernseyman travels to France for
OL,4,Csurgery to avoid long wait times
OL,6,FA Guernseyman travelled to to get
OL,7,Fdouble knee replacements after
OL,8,Fspending five years on the island's
OL,9,Fwaiting list.
OL,11,FJonathan Travers first sought help for
OL,12,Fhis knees back in 2019 but was left on
OL,13,Fhigh doses of painkillers while
OL,14,Fwaiting for an operation.
OL,16,FJonathan told ITV News: "It is just
OL,17,Fnon-stop pain. I am on reasonable,
OL,18,Fwell-strong painkillers but I don't
OL,19,Flike taking them. I just have to, or I
OL,20,Fcan't move at all."
