OL,3,CGuernseyman travels to France for
OL,4,Csurgery to avoid long wait times
OL,6,FLast month, Jonathan travelled to
OL,7,FFrance for a double knee replacement
OL,8,Frather than continue to wait in .
OL,10,FJonathan was quoted #14,500 per knee
OL,11,Fprivately in Guernsey; in France, it
OL,12,Fcosts #8,500 for both.
OL,14,FHe said "My grandson is four and I
OL,15,Fcould not keep up with him, but now I
OL,16,Fcan. My granddaughter isn't walking
OL,17,Fyet, but now I can carry them."
OL,19,FHe added: "It's absolutely phenomenal."
