OL,6,FWaiting lists remain at static levels
OL,7,Fin Guernsey, despite the De Havilland
OL,8,Forthopaedic unit opening in 2022 to
OL,9,Freduce numbers.
OL,11,FPresident for Health and Social Care
OL,12,FGuernsey, Deputy Al Brouard, said:
OL,13,F"Last year was the most orthopaedic
OL,14,Fsurgeries that have ever happened in
OL,15,Four hospital.
OL,17,F"But the demand unfortunately is still
OL,18,Fthere and it will continue to rise."
